('anatomy', 'easy', 'What is the signature ear shape that distinguishes French Bulldogs?', 'Bat ears (upright and rounded)', 'Rose ears (folded back)', 'Button ears (folded forward)', 'Drop ears (hanging down)', 'French Bulldogs are famous for their large, upright "bat ears," which American breeders fought to make the breed standard.', NULL, 0, 1),
('anatomy', 'easy', 'What is the maximum weight for a French Bulldog according to the AKC standard?', '28 pounds (13 kg)', '35 pounds (16 kg)', '20 pounds (9 kg)', '40 pounds (18 kg)', 'The AKC breed standard specifies a weight not to exceed 28 pounds.', NULL, 0, 1),
